      "description": "This vehicle represents a distinguished opportunity for the driver who prioritizes mechanical integrity and functional excellence. Rigorously maintained and subjected to a comprehensive multi-point inspection, this unit demonstrates consistent performance and reliable engineering. The interior cabin remains well-preserved, and the exterior reflects a history of responsible ownership. This is an exemplary choice for those seeking a sophisticated, road-ready vehicle that delivers dependable service without compromise.",
      "price": 31500.0,
